whisking for ten minutes.

376
00:17:38,022 --> 00:17:41,247
If your hand starts to spasm,
it means you're doing it right.

377
00:18:06,609 --> 00:18:08,875
Bree, I think it's been ten minutes!

378
00:18:08,875 --> 00:18:10,522
