393
00:19:20,404 --> 00:19:22,367
- Is that possible?
- I don't know.

394
00:19:22,497 --> 00:19:24,212
Well, then what's in the envelope?

395
00:19:25,106 --> 00:19:27,902
Maybe the cell phone or a
piece of the shovel handle.

396
00:19:27,902 --> 00:19:30,103
