and I'll do the rest.

403
00:19:43,121 --> 00:19:44,040
Got it.

404
00:19:45,996 --> 00:19:47,767
What if the briefcase is locked?

405
00:19:47,894 --> 00:19:50,375
I can pick locks. Yeah.

406
00:19:51,002 --> 00:19:53,597
